4KVrXJnxKvQgVik=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering user follow-up**\\n\\nI need to give the user an update regarding their question, \\\"修好了吗\\\" (Is it fixed?). I think I should say it's not yet resolved, but I found the root cause. I might suggest the next step, like installing ffmpeg or asking them to send an mp3 or wav sample. However, since installation has some complications, it's probably best to request the user to send a sample or give permission to install ffmpeg first.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 还没完全修好，但根因抓到了：**不是飞书发不出去，是 Noiz 直接把你这份 `.ogg/.opus` 参考样本判成 `invalid audio file`**，所以它吐出来的是一段 68 字节的报错内容，不是真音频。  \n\n最省事两条路，你选一个：\n1. **你再给本王发一份 mp3 或 wav 样本**，本王直接继续克隆  \n2. **你允许本王装/找转码工具**，我先把这份 opus 转成 wav 再喂给 Noiz","textSignature":"msg_093322766c08914b0169aea613bd4c819698cd603f1d490b41"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":166,"output":223,"cacheRead":68864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69253,"cost":{"input":0.0002905,"output":0.0031219999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0120512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0154637}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773053454126}}
