ed to these questions later on, but for now, I should focus on delivering a concise response. It’s essential to ensure clarity while keeping everything straightforward — I'll make sure I’m covering all the necessary points without overcomplicating things.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 能做，给你整一份像样的。先定 5 个参数，本王就开做：\n\n1. **风格**  \n- `科技蓝图（推荐）`  \n- `企业简洁`  \n- `手绘讲解`\n\n2. **受众**  \n- `通用观众（推荐）`  \n- `学员/初学者`  \n- `专家/合作方`\n\n3. **页数**  \n- `8 页（推荐）`  \n- `6 页`  \n- `10 页`\n\n4. **大纲要不要先给你看**  \n- `要（推荐）`  \n- `不要，直接做`\n\n5. **图片提示词要不要先给你看**  \n- `要`  \n- `不要（推荐）`\n\n你直接按 `1-科技蓝图，2-通用观众，3-8页，4-不要，5-不要` 这种格式回我。","textSignature":"msg_093322766c08914b0169aec53f42108196b30479f942fa8228"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":5886,"output":247,"cacheRead":73728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79861,"cost":{"input":0.0103005,"output":0.003458,"cacheRead":0.0129024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0266609}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773061432897}}
