{"type":"message","id":"89f8cd58","parentId":"a93aff05","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:18:18.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 懂了，你要的不是传统 PPT 文件，而是**一页页图片式 PPT**，像下午那种能直接发群、发朋友圈、发飞书的视觉页。  \n本王现在就按这个方向重做——给你产出 **PNG 图片版**，需要的话再顺手给你合成 PPTX。","textSignature":"msg_093322766c08914b0169aec89865308196a6f1883b0f74e9ca"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":85411,"output":83,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87030,"cost":{"input":0.14946925,"output":0.001162,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15090005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773062286491}}
{"type":"message","id":"b50540ba","parentId":"89f8cd58","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:18:49.702Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-09 21:18:49 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f [msg:om_x100b55d8c5453cacb2dffac1dd50583]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d8c5453cacb2dffac1dd50583\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 21:18 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n肯定要合成的，加油"}],"timestamp":1773062329697}}
